{"title":"在天津制钢厂","authors":["王琳"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":11,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天津制钢厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王琳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一　轧钢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑＠＠的……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条，一条，一条……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵，一朵，一朵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从熔炉里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从轧钢机上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从铁板上……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从粗大的手掌里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘旋，游泳，跳跃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出金属的声音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮了我们乌黑的眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塑像呵，一个个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨大的劳动的黑影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耸立在我们面前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的钢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的屋子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心熔化了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一团通红！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被火红的一片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发光，透明！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二　模范"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈明德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天早上六点半就进厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把修理部机器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦得干干净净"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“擦机器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比大人给小孩洗澡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不洗澡，病了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是大人的错。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈明德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱护机器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象爱护家里的孩子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"津钢报出版了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家围着报纸说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“好，括括叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧，老陈当了模范啦！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三　“麻烦”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丝钉工场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸模工人孙士锡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外号“麻烦”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身体高高的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厂里数一数二的球将，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶而也把＠跤高招儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由主任到小童工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没一个不爱同他逗了玩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“麻烦”，吃饭不带菜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捞到黄牛当马骑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胃口大得象水盆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟卷头抽完了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老赵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来一口，过过瘾！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“麻烦”拆烧公家竹筐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布告栏里登着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孙士锡记过一次”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“麻烦”心里烦得几天没睡觉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军代表再三鼓励"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他才算心平一些。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那夜，九月十四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丝部屋顶到处漏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“麻烦”自动报名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担任看电滚，掏水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要加班费。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十点，回家拿饭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老婆问："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不是下班了吗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么又拿呢？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“加班！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“今晚大雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里都漏了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么办？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“家里怎么办，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厂里又怎么办呢？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“麻烦”匆匆地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着饽饽进厂了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四　报告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热烈地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长长地掌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"委员讲话了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“四六年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石撕破了政协决议"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向解放区进攻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们把马丁炉天纤上不加油"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧毁电滚子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把炉顶砖掉在炉里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫炉底捣乱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们破坏敌人工厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫中国人民多活几条命！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“解放前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国民党要把马丁炉搬到上海去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们机械场朱鸿典同志出头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋匪军要把朱鸿典抓走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要抓朱鸿典"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们一齐去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结果，国民党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乖乖地输了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“解放了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去一个人拉七十斤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在拉到七百多斤啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张贵同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把脚烫坏还坚持工作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人家张贵还这么干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺们没有说的……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这些，一句话归总"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是党的领导！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五　一天的生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天的生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们看到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一幅新中国的远景！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们每个人要成为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枕木、砂石、铁轨、轮子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让新民主主义的列车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驶向美丽的远方去！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}